    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款原子朋克/电子摇摆风格的自动拳击游戏中，努力攀升排名，跻身最伟大机械战士之列!🎵 选择国家，并为你的拳击手配备各种技能、联赛腰带和机器人，这些要么体现为不同的行为特征，要么会影响拳击手的速度、力量及耐力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/370e198b6626c7f759d0a3307921b6b8.poster.avif?t=1760547039\" width=470 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/370e198b6626c7f759d0a3307921b6b8.webm?t=1760547039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/370e198b6626c7f759d0a3307921b6b8.mp4?t=1760547039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在拳击手身后，会有一个忠实的团队进行操控并执行基本攻击。你需要管理他们的指令，补充系统资源，进行战略性闪避，并通过与音乐节拍同步的轻节奏挑战来加载和激活技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/c3e8df3ba80cb6dfebb141afddd21199.poster.avif?t=1760547039\" width=334 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/c3e8df3ba80cb6dfebb141afddd21199.webm?t=1760547039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/c3e8df3ba80cb6dfebb141afddd21199.mp4?t=1760547039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机器人的组件可能会在对手的重击下受损甚至损坏。幸运的是，你可以利用中场休息时间进行修复。同样，在战斗中晕眩的队员也会在休息时间苏醒，恢复他们提供的角色特定加成（如船长、驾驶员、武器或系统）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/8e63b548f13f981829e766f59371c41e.poster.avif?t=1760547039\" width=300 height=231 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/8e63b548f13f981829e766f59371c41e.webm?t=1760547039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系统血量耗尽时会开始倒计时，给倒下的机器人10秒时间重启，未能重启则算输。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在职业模式中，你将通过一系列每日管理活动赚取资源，用来解锁新的机器人部件、机器人技能和团队被动技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211280/extras/5ddc076065d8ee62d96e9b08197688c6.avif?t=1760547039\" width=350 height=340 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到电波拳击联赛的主场——恩普鲁姆体育场！</p>",
